156
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,590
OK, good question.

157
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:10,000
Good to clarify that.

158
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,410
So let's keep going.

159
00:09:11,410 --> 00:09:15,480
And right now, we have access
