2145
02:07:55,710 --> 02:07:58,920
that can actually clean
and escape the data

2146
02:07:58,920 --> 02:08:02,610
that we might want to insert into our
queries or our statements over there

2147
02:08:02,610 --> 02:08:03,810
too.

2148
02:08:03,810 --> 02:08:06,660
Good question.

